  //     ERR_VM_MODULE_NOT_MODULE issue from AWS SDK lazy provider
  //     loading, fixed by setting static credentials below)
  //   - the EVENT parsing path
  //   - withErrorHandling reaching its catch block + log + process.exit

  // Provide fake static AWS credentials so the SDK's
  // @aws-sdk/credential-provider-node does NOT try to lazy-load any
  // sub-providers via dynamic import(). Jest's experimental ESM loader
  // throws ERR_VM_MODULE_NOT_MODULE on those dynamic imports.
